## `has_any(conn, inode) -> bool`
<!-- checksum: xattrs-8 -->

### Purpose
Test-introspection helper. True if any xattrs exist for the inode. Used by `fs._row_exists("xattrs", inode)`.

### Implementation Notes

```python
def has_any(conn, inode):
    row = conn.execute(
        "SELECT 1 FROM xattrs WHERE inode = ? LIMIT 1", (inode,)
    ).fetchone()
    return row is not None
```

